..::Requires to run::..
* ffmpeq is used for the recording
* libqt4

..::Requires to build (NOTE: these are openSUSE 12.1 package names)::..
desktop-file-utils, libqt4-devel, gcc-c++, make, gcc46

..::How to build/compile::..
* cd source
* qmake FDesktopRecorder.pro
* make